label: An address delivered before the Calliopean and Polytechnic Societies of the State Military Academy, at the annual commencement, November 18th, 1847.
description: Typewritten version of the address given by Hon. S.W. Trotti to the Calliopean and Polytechnic Societies of the South Carolina Military Academy in 1847. Much emphasis is on state supported education and the importance of the free school system.
